{"tid":1986600,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"循還貸款騙案之你問我答（一）","createTime":"2020-04-24T02:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T00:46:47.000Z","uid":21356,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4a2c90732b24fb4c4a6ddd187df57d52e009f732","tid":1986600,"uid":21356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家好呀   <br />\n呢排經濟差左 好多人想借私人貸款去應急<br />\n大量騙徒應運而生<br />\n<br />\n識唔少人已經俾人呃左10K-200K<br />\n<br />\n一般騙案手法如下：<br />\n偽裝成某某銀行私人貸款部打黎向你推銷最新既私人貸款<br />\n超低息  抗疫良心貸款<br />\n但一定話你入息唔夠批啦  係銀行資產唔夠啦<br />\n<br />\n要求你提供一筆資金去   某某投資公司開立一個投資帳戶然後   要求投資公司發出資產証明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能你就會問啦  點解要去第二間公司開投資帳戶？<br />\n騙徒會指出   呢間公司其實都係某某銀行集團旗下子公司  唔洗擔心    然後就會用WhatsApp  Send一個偽造既某某銀行客戶經理卡片俾你    令你放低戒心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實你仔細啲睇    佢個Email  Address個名 同佢卡片上既中英文名係唔相同   英文名可能叫Peter  但 Email上個名可能係Rayas咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後 佢就會專登揀啲你好唔得既時間黎約你開戶口<br />\n  <br />\n記得帶埋現金呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔帶佢邊有錢呃你<br />\n<br />\n當你話唔得閒就中哂佢計啦    <br />\n佢會叫你交現金俾佢幫你開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後開張假收據俾你<br />\n<br />\n當你俾左現金佢    然後就沒有然後了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後受害人先會鬼拍後尾枕去  某某銀行核實該客戶經理既身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁當然啦    某某銀行係無呢位職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後受害人就會發現被騙 <br />\n啲錢就掉哂落咸水海  Sofar 未聽過追得翻    <br />\n因為係現金俾佢    加埋太空卡     <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係發問環節：<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好係呢個Post到 Blame The Victim  <br />\n而家呢個時勢借錢既 通常都係急用    佢地心急既心態被人利用我都可以理解    只係處理件事既次序錯左   應該先打起某某銀行/ 走落銀行核實身份先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盡量秒覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11ebf2d80613bdd794a40bb47bb621ef647b84a","tid":1986600,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:54:41.000Z","msg":"冇睇警訓？<br />\n雖然黑警好撚柒<br />\n但睇呢個節目 真係可以減少被騙<br />\n呢d騙案 真係過幾個星期就重演一單"},{"pid":"3e49b81325987381a5a78a97bf65e8f2f7671807","tid":1986600,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:55:04.000Z","msg":"樓主上咗幾多條狗乸 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba82050f0f4a9430b6306e3984d4dac391f6a631","tid":1986600,"uid":21356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b11ebf2d80613bdd794a40bb47bb621ef647b84a","tid":1986600,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:54:41.000Z","msg":"冇睇警訓？<br />\n雖然黑警好撚柒<br />\n但睇呢個節目 真係可以減少被騙<br />\n呢d騙案 真係過幾個星期就重演一單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   有人同我講  18222  警察果個防欺詐熱線叫佢落銀行搞"},{"pid":"8cac667ea1de26024b51588e4aecd29f98c6e567","tid":1986600,"uid":21356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e49b81325987381a5a78a97bf65e8f2f7671807","tid":1986600,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:55:04.000Z","msg":"樓主上咗幾多條狗乸 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /